# Local Supabase stack – Codespaces
# Supabase is proxied through Vite at /__supabase so only port 3000 needs to be public.
# Relative path: the client resolves it against window.location.origin at runtime,
# so the app works identically whether accessed via localhost or the Codespaces URL.
